727674f-a.title: Queens: Parsons Boulevard - Willets Point Boulevard
727674f-a.text:
Parsons Boulevard, north from near Willets Point
Boulevard, showing the entrance to the village of
Whitestone. The sigh on the left reads: Welcome to
WThitestone -- Follow the Arrows and See the Town.
The Boulevard is the former Fourth Avenue.
P. L. Sperr  April 13, 1927
NO REPRODUCTIONS

727675f-a.title: Queens: Parsons Boulevard - Willets Point Boulevard
727675f-a.text:
Parsons Boulevard, at the S.E. corner of Willets Point
Boulevard, showing a tree nursery and hot houses, one of a
group of about seven or eight located in this area. The view
is across the Old Country Club Golf links.
P. L. Sperr  April 13, 1927
